{"type":null,"faqId":32985,"title":"通话时对方反馈声音小或无声（无送话）如何处理？","answer":"<html>\n<head>\n<META http-equiv=\"Content-Type\" content=\"text/html; charset=UTF-8\">\n<style type=\"text/css\">.b1{white-space-collapsing:preserve;}\n.d1{margin: 1.18125in 0.7875in 1.18125in 0.7875in;}\n.s1{color:black;}\n.p1{margin-left:0.39375in;margin-top:0.11111111in;margin-bottom:0.11111111in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:10pt;}\n</style>\n</head>\n<body class=\"b1\">\n<div  >\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s1\">1.手持模式通话时通过左下方主MIC发送语音，请确认通话过程中手指是否堵住Mic拾音孔；</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s1\">2.手持模式通话时，华为采用双MIC降噪技术提升通话清晰度，为您带来更好的通话体验，会将距离主Mic较远的声音视为噪音，进行自动滤除，因此请保持正常距离（主mic距离人嘴10cm以内）通话。</span>\n</p>\n</div>\n</body>\n</html>\n","faqTypeId":137,"faqType":"通话与联系人","useful":0,"unUseful":5,"languageId":2,"languageName":"zh_cn","faqCode":"7687","faqTypeCode":"Handsets-Calls-contacts","isTop":"0","moduleCode":"faq","productId":null,"productCode":null,"postDate":1436748466000,"seriesProductName":"PLK-AL10,PLK-CL00,PLK-TL00,PLK-TL01H,PLK-UL00","visitedTimes":124,"isUsefulFlag":null,"score":0,"times":0,"imageList":null,"displayType":"text","justView":"0","fileName":null,"filePath":null,"imagePath":null,"imageName":null,"productIdList":null,"curPage":null,"pageSize":null,"siteCode":null,"statusFlag":"Publish","returnCode":0,"totalRows":null,"keywords":"通话,音量小","avgScore":0.0,"createDate":null,"totalPages":null}